oot/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/13-系统管理.md\n/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/14-二开发展深入说明.md\n/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/14-插件开发深入.md\n/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/15-报表开发实战.md\n/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/16-前端开发进阶.md","cwd":"/root/clawd-bingbu"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227285540}}
