{"type":"message","id":"f783567a","parentId":"e181a647","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:54:46.733Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_277667e6bae24c1087c91bcc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 金蝶云苍穹插件开发文档\n\n**版本**: 金蝶云苍穹 v8.x  \n**文档ID**: JJC-20260320-001  \n**创建时间**: 2026-03-20\n\n---\n\n## 📋 概述\n\n金蝶云苍穹提供灵活的插件（Plugin）机制，允许开发者扩展平台功能，自定义业务逻辑，实现高度定制化的企业应用。\n\n## 🎯 苍穹主要优势\n\n### 1. 技术优势\n\n#### 1.1 微服务架构\n- **优势**: 模块化部署，按需扩展\n- **特点**:\n  - 独立部署：每个插件独立部署，互不影响\n  - 弹性扩展：根据业务需求动态扩容\n  - 故障隔离：单个插件故障不影响整体\n- **示例架构**:\n```javascript\n// 插件独立部署配置\nconst PluginDeployment = {\n  pluginId: \"kdev_custom_plugin\",\n  pluginName: \"自定义插件\",\n  version: \"1.0.0\",\n  deploy: {\n    type: \"standalone\",  // 独立部署\n    resources: {\n      cpu: \"2核\",\n      memory: \"4GB\",\n      storage: \"20GB\"\n    }\n  },\n  dependencies: [\n    {\n      pluginId: \"core_framework\",\n      version: \">= 8.0.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n};\n```\n\n**C# 示例**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Plugin.Core;\n\n[PluginMetadata(\n    Id = \"kdev_custom_plugin\",\n    Name = \"自定义插件\",\n    Version = \"1.0.0\",\n    Description = \"自定义业务功能插件\",\n    Author = \"开发者\",\n    DeployMode = DeployMode.Standalone  // 独立部署\n)]\npublic class CustomPlugin : PluginBase\n{\n    public CustomPlugin()\n    {\n        Dependencies = new List<PluginDependency>\n        {\n            new PluginDependency \n            { \n                PluginId = \"core_framework\",\n                Version = new Version(\"8.0.0\")\n            }\n        };\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 1.2 低代码开发\n- **优势**: 快速开发，降低技术门槛\n- **特点**:\n  - 可视化设计：拖拽式界面设计器\n  - 配置化开发：通过配置而非编码\n  - 自动生成代码：减少手工编码量\n- **开发效率**: 提升50-70%\n\n**可视化设计器示例（React）**:\n```jsx\nimport React from 'react';\nimport { FormDesigner, ComponentPalette } from 'k3cloud-designer';\n\nconst CustomFormDesign = () => {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"designer-container\">\n      <ComponentPalette />\n      <FormDesigner\n        canvas=\"main\"\n        components={[\n          { type: 'input', label: '文本输入' },\n          { type: 'date', label: '日期选择' },\n          { type: 'select', label: '下拉选择' },\n          { type: 'table', label: '数据表格' }\n        ]}\n      />\n    </div>\n  );\n};\n```\n\n**低代码配置示例（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"formId\": \"kdev_custom_form\",\n  \"formConfig\": {\n    \"designer\": \"visual\",\n    \"autoGenerate\": true,\n    \"fields\": [\n      {\n        \"componentType\": \"input\",\n        \"props\": {\n          \"label\": \"用户名\",\n          \"placeholder\": \"请输入用户名\",\n          \"validation\": {\n            \"required\": true,\n            \"maxLength\": 50\n          }\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"componentType\": \"date\",\n        \"props\": {\n          \"label\": \"创建日期\",\n          \"format\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n          \"validation\": {\n            \"required\": true\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 低代码引擎**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.LowCode.Engine;\n\npublic class LowCodeFormEngine\n{\n    private readonly IComponentFactory _componentFactory;\n    \n    public LowCodeFormEngine(IComponentFactory componentFactory)\n    {\n        _componentFactory = componentFactory;\n    }\n    \n    public IForm BuildForm(string formId)\n    {\n        var config = FormConfigRepository.GetConfig(formId);\n        var form = new DynamicForm(formId);\n        \n        foreach (var field in config.Fields)\n        {\n            var component = _componentFactory.CreateComponent(\n                field.ComponentType, \n                field.Props\n            );\n            form.AddComponent(component);\n        }\n        \n        return form;\n    }\n}\n\n// 自动生成的表单验证\npublic class AutoGeneratedValidator : IFormValidator\n{\n    public ValidationResult Validate(IForm form, object data)\n    {\n        var result = new ValidationResult();\n        \n        foreach (var field in form.Fields)\n        {\n            if (field.Props.Validation.Required)\n            {\n                if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(data[field.Name]))\n                {\n                    result.AddFieldError(field.Name, $\"{field.Label}为必填项\");\n                }\n            }\n            \n            if (field.Props.Validation.MaxLength != null &&\n                data[field.Name]?.ToString().Length > field.Props.Validation.MaxLength)\n            {\n                result.AddFieldError(field.Name, \n                    $\"{field.Label}长度不能超过{field.Props.Validation.MaxLength}\");\n            }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return result;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n[804 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227286727}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e4e936d","parentId":"f783567a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:54:48.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我继续读取插件开发文档的更多内容，特别是关于插件接口的部分。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_661dc00a23f94b0d89ab1db0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/03-插件开发.md","offset":200,"limit":200}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1161,"output":78,"cacheRead":16865,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774227286734}}
{"type":"message","id":"230f849b","parentId":"8e4e936d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:54:48.046Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_661dc00a23f94b0d89ab1db0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"```\n\n### 2. 业务优势\n\n#### 2.1 行业预置方案\n- **优势**: 开箱即用，快速上线\n- **行业方案**: 制造、零售、服务、建筑等\n\n**行业模板配置（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"industryTemplates\": [\n    {\n      \"industryId\": \"manufacturing\",\n      \"industryName\": \"制造业\",\n      \"templates\": [\n        {\n          \"templateId\": \"mfg_production\",\n          \"templateName\": \"生产管理\",\n          \"modules\": [\n            \"bom_management\",\n            \"production_planning\",\n            \"quality_control\",\n            \"equipment_maintenance\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"templateId\": \"mfg_inventory\",\n          \"templateName\": \"库存管理\",\n          \"modules\": [\n            \"inventory_control\",\n            \"warehouse_management\",\n            \"procurement\",\n            \"supplier_management\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"industryId\": \"retail\",\n      \"industryName\": \"零售业\",\n      \"templates\": [\n        {\n          \"templateId\": \"retail_pos\",\n          \"templateName\": \"POS系统\",\n          \"modules\": [\n            \"sales_management\",\n            \"member_management\",\n            \"promotion_management\",\n            \"data_analysis\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**C# 行业方案加载**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Industry;\n\npublic class IndustryTemplateService\n{\n    private readonly ITemplateRepository _templateRepository;\n    \n    public async Task<IndustryTemplate> LoadTemplateAsync(string industryId)\n    {\n        var template = await _templateRepository.GetByIdAsync(industryId);\n        \n        // 自动部署行业模板\n        await DeployModulesAsync(template.Modules);\n        \n        // 初始化基础数据\n        await InitializeBaseDataAsync(template.BaseData);\n        \n        // 配置业务规则\n        await ConfigureBusinessRulesAsync(template.Rules);\n        \n        return template;\n    }\n    \n    private async Task DeployModulesAsync(List<string> modules)\n    {\n        foreach (var moduleId in modules)\n        {\n            var module = await ModuleRepository.GetByIdAsync(moduleId);\n            await ModuleDeployer.DeployAsync(module);\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n#### 2.2 智能化能力\n- **优势**: AI赋能，提升业务价值\n- **AI功能**:\n  - 智能预测：销量预测、库存预测\n  - 智能推荐：产品推荐、供应商推荐\n  - 智能分析：数据分析、异常检测\n  - 智能助手：自然语言交互\n\n**AI智能分析示例（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"aiService\": \"sales_prediction\",\n  \"config\": {\n    \"model\": \"time_series_forecast\",\n    \"parameters\": {\n      \"lookback_days\": 90,\n      \"forecast_days\": 30,\n      \"confidence_interval\": 0.95\n    },\n    \"input\": {\n      \"dataSource\": \"sales_orders\",\n      \"features\": [\n        \"sales_amount\",\n        \"quantity\",\n        \"customer_id\",\n        \"product_id\",\n        \"date\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"output\": {\n    \"predictions\": [\n      {\n        \"date\": \"2026-04-01\",\n        \"predicted_sales\": 150000,\n        \"confidence\": 0.92,\n        \"upper_bound\": 165000,\n        \"lower_bound\": 135000\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# AI服务调用**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.AI.Services;\n\npublic class SalesPredictionService\n{\n    private readonly IAIService _aiService;\n    \n    public SalesPredictionService(IAIService aiService)\n    {\n        _aiService = aiService;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<SalesPrediction> PredictSalesAsync(\n        string productId, \n        int forecastDays = 30)\n    {\n        var request = new PredictionRequest\n        {\n            Model = \"time_series_forecast\",\n            Parameters = new PredictionParameters\n            {\n                LookbackDays = 90,\n                ForecastDays = forecastDays,\n                ConfidenceInterval = 0.95\n            },\n            Input = new PredictionInput\n            {\n                DataSource = \"sales_orders\",\n                Features = new List<string>\n                {\n                    \"sales_amount\",\n                    \"quantity\",\n                    \"customer_id\",\n                    \"product_id\",\n                    \"date\"\n                }\n            }\n        };\n        \n        var response = await _aiService.PredictAsync(request);\n        \n        return new SalesPrediction\n        {\n            ProductId = productId,\n            ForecastDays = forecastDays,\n            Predictions = response.Output.Predictions,\n            Confidence = CalculateConfidence(response.Output.Predictions)\n        };\n    }\n}\n\npublic class SalesPrediction\n{\n    public string ProductId { get; set; }\n    public int ForecastDays { get; set; }\n    public List<DailyPrediction> Predictions { get; set; }\n    public double Confidence { get; set; }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 平台优势\n\n\n[605 more lines in file. Use offset=400 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227288040}}
