{"type":"message","id":"1a2bd860","parentId":"10eb6cd0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:02:40.655Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好，现在让我创建一个简单的使用示例文件，展示如何使用这些插件系统。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3cf7f9c569894cbbaae27711","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 云天佑插件系统使用示例\n\n本文档展示如何使用云天佑插件系统的各种功能。\n\n---\n\n## 目录\n1. [表单插件示例](#表单插件示例)\n2. [列表插件示例](#列表插件示例)\n3. [操作插件示例](#操作插件示例)\n4. [工作流插件示例](#工作流插件示例)\n5. [转换插件示例](#转换插件示例)\n6. [报表插件示例](#报表插件示例)\n7. [元数据服务示例](#元数据服务示例)\n8. [通用数据服务示例](#通用数据服务示例)\n\n---\n\n## 表单插件示例\n\n### 基础表单插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"sales_order_form_plugin\",\n        Name = \"销售订单表单插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\",\n        Description = \"销售订单表单业务逻辑扩展\"\n    )]\n    public class SalesOrderFormPlugin : PluginBase, IFormPlugin\n    {\n        public void OnLoad(FormLoadEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 表单加载时设置默认值\n            e.DataModel.SetValue(\"order_date\", DateTime.Now);\n            e.DataModel.SetValue(\"status\", \"draft\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnValueChanged(FormValueChangedEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 价格变更时自动计算折扣\n            if (e.FieldKey == \"price\" && e.NewValue != null)\n            {\n                var price = Convert.ToDecimal(e.NewValue);\n                var discount = price * 0.9m;\n                e.FormView.SetValue(\"discount\", discount);\n            }\n\n            // 数量变更时自动计算总价\n            if (e.FieldKey == \"quantity\" && e.NewValue != null)\n            {\n                var quantity = Convert.ToInt32(e.NewValue);\n                var price = e.FormView.GetValue<decimal>(\"price\");\n                var total = quantity * price;\n                e.FormView.SetValue(\"total_amount\", total);\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeSave(FormBeforeSaveEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 保存前验证\n            var customerId = e.DataModel.GetValue<string>(\"customer_id\");\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(customerId))\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"客户不能为空\";\n                return;\n            }\n\n            var amount = e.DataModel.GetValue<decimal>(\"total_amount\");\n            if (amount <= 0)\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"订单金额必须大于0\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterSave(FormAfterSaveEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 保存后记录日志\n            Console.WriteLine($\"订单已保存: {e.DataModel.GetValue<string>(\"order_no\")}\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeDelete(FormBeforeDeleteEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 删除前检查是否已审核\n            // 这里可以添加业务逻辑\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeSubmit(FormBeforeSubmitEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 提交前验证\n            var status = e.DataModel.GetValue<string>(\"status\");\n            if (status != \"draft\")\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"只能提交草稿状态的订单\";\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 列表插件示例\n\n### 列表插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"customer_list_plugin\",\n        Name = \"客户列表插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\"\n    )]\n    public class CustomerListPlugin : PluginBase, IListPlugin\n    {\n        public void OnLoad(ListLoadEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 列表加载时添加默认过滤\n            e.ListModel.SetFilter(new List<FilterCondition>\n            {\n                new FilterCondition\n                {\n                    FieldName = \"status\",\n                    Operator = FilterOperator.Equal,\n                    Value = \"active\"\n                }\n            });\n        }\n\n        public void OnSelectionChanged(ListSelectionChangedEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 选中行变更时更新统计\n            Console.WriteLine($\"选中了 {e.SelectedRowIds.Count} 条记录\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnRowDoubleClick(ListRowDoubleClickEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 双击打开详情\n            Console.WriteLine($\"打开客户详情: {e.RowData.GetValue<string>(\"name\")}\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnToolbarButtonClick(ListToolbarButtonClickEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 工具栏按钮点击\n            if (e.ButtonKey == \"batch_activate\")\n            {\n                if (e.SelectedRowIds.Count == 0)\n                {\n                    e.Cancel = true;\n                    e.ErrorMessage = \"请先选择要激活的客户\";\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeLoadData(ListBeforeLoadDataEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 数据加载前修改过滤条件\n            if (e.SortField == \"create_time\")\n            {\n                e.SortDirection = SortDirection.Descending;\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterLoadData(ListAfterLoadDataEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 数据加载后处理\n            Console.WriteLine($\"加载了 {e.TotalCount} 条记录\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 操作插件示例\n\n### 自定义操作插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"custom_operation_plugin\",\n        Name = \"自定义操作插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\"\n    )]\n    public class CustomOperationPlugin : PluginBase, IOperationPlugin\n    {\n        public void BeforeExecute(OperationBeforeExecuteEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 操作执行前检查\n            if (e.OperationKey == \"approve_order\")\n            {\n                var amount = e.Context.DataRows[0].GetValue<decimal>(\"total_amount\");\n                if (amount > 100000)\n                {\n                    e.Cancel = true;\n                    e.ErrorMessage = \"金额超过10万的订单需要高级审批\";\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterExecute(OperationAfterExecuteEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 操作执行后记录\n            Console.WriteLine($\"操作 {e.OperationKey} 执行完成\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnValidate(OperationValidateEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 操作验证\n            if (e.OperationKey == \"delete_order\")\n            {\n                var status = e.Context.DataRows[0].GetValue<string>(\"status\");\n                if (status == \"approved\")\n                {\n                    e.ValidationResult.AddError(\"status\", \"已审核的订单不能删除\");\n                    e.Cancel = true;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void OnException(OperationExceptionEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 操作异常处理\n            Console.WriteLine($\"操作 {e.OperationKey} 发生异常: {e.Exception.Message}\");\n            e.ExceptionHandled = true;\n            e.CustomErrorMessage = \"操作失败，请联系管理员\";\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 工作流插件示例\n\n### 工作流插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"approval_workflow_plugin\",\n        Name = \"审批工作流插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\"\n    )]\n    public class ApprovalWorkflowPlugin : PluginBase, IWorkflowPlugin\n    {\n        public void BeforeStart(WorkflowBeforeStartEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 流程启动前验证\n            var amount = e.BusinessData.GetValue<decimal>(\"total_amount\");\n            if (amount <= 0)\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"订单金额必须大于0\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterStart(WorkflowAfterStartEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 流程启动后通知\n            Console.WriteLine($\"流程已启动: {e.InstanceId}\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeNodeEnter(WorkflowBeforeNodeEnterEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 节点到达前检查\n            Console.WriteLine($\"流程将进入节点: {e.NodeName}\");\n        }\n\n        public void AfterNodeEnter(WorkflowAfterNodeEnterEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 节点到达后通知处理人\n            foreach (var assignee in e.Assignees)\n            {\n                Console.WriteLine($\"通知 {assignee} 处理: {e.NodeName}\");\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeNodeLeave(WorkflowBeforeNodeLeaveEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 节点离开前验证\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(e.Comment))\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"请填写审批意见\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeApprove(WorkflowBeforeApproveEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 审批前检查\n            var status = e.BusinessData.GetValue<string>(\"status\");\n            if (status != \"pending\")\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"只能审批待审核的订单\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterApprove(WorkflowAfterApproveEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 审批后更新状态\n            e.BusinessData.SetValue(\"status\", \"approved\");\n            Console.WriteLine($\"订单已由 {e.Approver.UserName} 审批通过\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeReject(WorkflowBeforeRejectEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 拒绝前验证\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(e.Reason))\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"请填写拒绝原因\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterReject(WorkflowAfterRejectEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 拒绝后更新状态\n            e.BusinessData.SetValue(\"status\", \"rejected\");\n            Console.WriteLine($\"订单被拒绝: {e.Reason}\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnCompleted(WorkflowCompletedEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 流程完成\n            Console.WriteLine($\"流程完成，耗时: {e.DurationSeconds}秒\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnCanceled(WorkflowCanceledEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 流程取消\n            Console.WriteLine($\"流程被取消: {e.Reason}\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 转换插件示例\n\n### 数据转换插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"order_convert_plugin\",\n        Name = \"订单转换插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\"\n    )]\n    public class OrderConvertPlugin : PluginBase, IConvertPlugin\n    {\n        public void BeforeConvert(ConvertBeforeConvertEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 转换前验证\n            if (e.Source.GetValue<string>(\"status\") != \"approved\")\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"只能转换已审核的订单\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterConvert(ConvertAfterConvertEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 转换后记录\n            Console.WriteLine($\"订单 {e.Source.GetValue<string>(\"order_no\")} 已转换为发货单\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeMapField(ConvertBeforeMapFieldEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 字段映射前自定义\n            if (e.SourceField == \"order_date\" && e.TargetField == \"ship_date\")\n            {\n                // 延期3天发货\n                var date = Convert.ToDateTime(e.SourceValue);\n                e.CustomTargetValue = date.AddDays(3);\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterMapField(ConvertAfterMapFieldEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 字段映射后处理\n            Console.WriteLine($\"字段映射: {e.SourceField} -> {e.TargetField}\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeCreateTarget(ConvertBeforeCreateTargetEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 目标对象创建前验证\n            Console.WriteLine($\"准备创建目标对象: {e.TargetType}\");\n        }\n\n        public void OnValidate(ConvertValidateEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 验证转换结果\n            var targetId = e.Target.GetValue<string>(\"id\");\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(targetId))\n            {\n                e.ValidationResult.AddError(\"id\", \"目标ID不能为空\");\n            }\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 报表插件示例\n\n### 报表插件\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions;\nusing Tianyou.Plugin.Abstractions.Plugins;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Plugins.Examples\n{\n    [PluginMetadata(\n        Id = \"sales_report_plugin\",\n        Name = \"销售报表插件\",\n        Version = \"1.0.0\"\n    )]\n    public class SalesReportPlugin : PluginBase, IReportPlugin\n    {\n        public void BeforeQuery(ReportBeforeQueryEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 查询前添加过滤\n            if (!e.Parameters.ContainsKey(\"start_date\"))\n            {\n                e.Parameters[\"start_date\"] = DateTime.Now.AddMonths(-1);\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterQuery(ReportAfterQueryEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 查询后处理\n            Console.WriteLine($\"查询了 {e.TotalCount} 条记录，耗时 {e.ExecutionTimeMs}ms\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeCalculate(ReportBeforeCalculateEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 计算前验证\n            if (e.RawData.Count == 0)\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"没有数据可计算\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterCalculate(ReportAfterCalculateEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 计算后汇总\n            var total = e.CalculatedData.Sum(d => d.GetValue<decimal>(\"amount\"));\n            e.SummaryData[\"total_amount\"] = total;\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeRender(ReportBeforeRenderEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 渲染前检查\n            Console.WriteLine($\"准备渲染报表，格式: {e.Format}\");\n        }\n\n        public void BeforeExport(ReportBeforeExportEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 导出前检查\n            if (e.Data.Count > 10000)\n            {\n                e.Cancel = true;\n                e.ErrorMessage = \"导出数据不能超过10000条\";\n            }\n        }\n\n        public void AfterExport(ReportAfterExportEventArgs e)\n        {\n            // 导出后记录\n            Console.WriteLine($\"报表已导出: {e.FilePath}，大小: {e.FileSize}字节\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 元数据服务示例\n\n### 表单元数据使用\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Core.Abstractions.Metadata;\n\n// 创建表单元数据\nvar formMetadata = new FormMetadata\n{\n    FormId = \"sales_order\",\n    FormName = \"销售订单\",\n    EntityId = \"t_so_order\",\n    FormType = FormType.Normal\n};\n\n// 添加字段\nformMetadata.AddField(new FieldMetadata\n{\n    FieldKey = \"order_no\",\n    FieldName = \"订单号\",\n    DataType = FieldDataType.String,\n    Length = 50,\n    IsRequired = true,\n    IsUnique = true\n});\n\nformMetadata.AddField(new FieldMetadata\n{\n    FieldKey = \"order_date\",\n    FieldName = \"订单日期\",\n    DataType = FieldDataType.Date,\n    IsRequired = true,\n    DefaultValue = DateTime.Now\n});\n\n// 获取字段\nvar orderNoField = formMetadata.GetField(\"order_no\");\n\n// 获取必填字段\nvar requiredFields = formMetadata.GetRequiredFields();\n```\n\n### 实体元数据使用\n\n```csharp\n// 创建实体元数据\nvar entityMetadata = new EntityMetadata\n{\n    EntityId = \"customer\",\n    EntityName = \"客户\",\n    TableName = \"t_customer\",\n    PrimaryKey = \"customer_id\",\n    EnableAudit = true,\n    EnableSoftDelete = true\n};\n\n// 添加字段\nentityMetadata.AddField(new FieldMetadata\n{\n    FieldKey = \"customer_id\",\n    FieldName = \"客户ID\",\n    DataType = FieldDataType.String,\n    Length = 50,\n    IsRequired = true\n});\n\n// 添加索引\nentityMetadata.AddIndex(new IndexMetadata\n{\n    IndexName = \"idx_customer_name\",\n    FieldNames = new List<string> { \"customer_name\" },\n    IsUnique = false\n});\n\n// 添加关系\nentityMetadata.AddRelation(new RelationMetadata\n{\n    RelationName = \"orders\",\n    FieldKey = \"customer_id\",\n    RelationType = RelationType.OneToMany,\n    RelatedEntity = \"sales_order\",\n    RelatedField = \"customer_id\",\n    CascadeDelete = false\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 通用数据服务示例\n\n### 查询构建器使用\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Core.Abstractions.Services;\n\n// 构建简单查询\nvar query = QueryBuilder.Create(\"customer\")\n    .Equal(\"status\", \"active\")\n    .GreaterThan(\"credit\", 1000)\n    .OrderBy(\"create_time\")\n    .Paged(1, 20);\n\n// 构建复杂查询\nvar complexQuery = QueryBuilder.Create(\"sales_order\")\n    .GreaterThanOrEqual(\"order_date\", startDate)\n    .LessThanOrEqual(\"order_date\", endDate)\n    .In(\"status\", new List<object> { \"approved\", \"shipped\" })\n    .Contains(\"customer_name\", \"张\")\n    .OrderByDescending(\"total_amount\")\n    .Paged(pageIndex, pageSize);\n\n// 执行查询\nvar result = await _genericDataService.QueryPagedAsync(\"sales_order\", query.Build());\nConsole.WriteLine($\"共 {result.TotalCount} 条记录，当前页 {result.Data.Count} 条\");\n```\n\n### 过滤条件解析使用\n\n```csharp\n// 从JSON解析\nvar json = @\"\n[\n    {\"\"FieldName\"\":\"\"status\"\",\"\"Operator\"\":\"\"Equal\"\",\"\"Value\"\":\"\"active\"\"},\n    {\"\"FieldName\"\":\"\"name\"\",\"\"Operator\"\":\"\"Contains\"\",\"\"Value\"\":\"\"张\"\"}\n]\";\nvar filters = FilterParser.ParseFromJson(json);\n\n// 从字典解析\nvar dict = new Dictionary<string, object>\n{\n    { \"status_eq\", \"active\" },\n    { \"name_contains\", \"张\" },\n    { \"age_gte\", 18 }\n};\nvar filters = FilterParser.ParseFromDictionary(dict);\n\n// 从查询字符串解析\nvar queryString = \"status_eq=active&name_contains=张&age_gte=18\";\nvar filters = FilterParser.ParseFromQueryString(queryString);\n\n// 转换为SQL\nvar parameters = new Dictionary<string, object>();\nvar sql = FilterParser.ToSqlWhere(filters, parameters);\n// 输出: status = @param_xxx AND name LIKE @param_yyy AND age >= @param_zzz\n\n// 创建常用条件\nvar equalFilter = FilterParser.CreateEqual(\"status\", \"active\");\nvar containsFilter = FilterParser.CreateContains(\"name\", \"张\");\nvar inFilter = FilterParser.CreateIn(\"id\", new List<object> { \"1\", \"2\", \"3\" });\n```\n\n### 通用数据服务使用\n\n```csharp\n// 查询单条记录\nvar customer = await _genericDataService.QueryByIdAsync(\"customer\", \"C001\");\n\n// 查询多条记录\nvar condition = new QueryCondition();\ncondition.AddFilter(new FilterCondition\n{\n    FieldName = \"status\",\n    Operator = FilterOperator.Equal,\n    Value = \"active\"\n});\nvar customers = await _genericDataService.QueryAsync(\"customer\", condition);\n\n// 分页查询\nvar pagedResult = await _genericDataService.QueryPagedAsync(\"customer\", condition);\nConsole.WriteLine($\"第 {pagedResult.PageIndex} 页，每页 {pagedResult.PageSize} 条，共 {pagedResult.TotalPages} 页\");\n\n// 新增记录\nvar newCustomer = new DynamicObject\n{\n    [\"customer_id\"] = \"C002\",\n    [\"customer_name\"] = \"张三\",\n    [\"status\"] = \"active\"\n};\nvar id = await _genericDataService.CreateAsync(\"customer\", newCustomer);\n\n// 更新记录\nnewCustomer[\"status\"] = \"inactive\";\nvar success = await _genericDataService.UpdateAsync(\"customer\", newCustomer);\n\n// 删除记录\nsuccess = await _genericDataService.DeleteAsync(\"customer\", \"C002\");\n\n// 统计记录数\nvar count = await _genericDataService.CountAsync(\"customer\", condition);\n\n// 判断记录是否存在\nvar exists = await _genericDataService.ExistsAsync(\"customer\", \"C001\");\n\n// 执行自定义查询\nvar sql = \"SELECT * FROM t_customer WHERE status = @status\";\nvar parameters = new Dictionary<string, object> { { \"status\", \"active\" } };\nvar results = await _genericDataService.ExecuteQueryAsync(sql, parameters);\n```\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n云天佑插件系统提供了完整的插件化开发能力，包括：\n\n1. **6种插件接口** - 覆盖表单、列表、操作、工作流、转换、报表等场景\n2. **元数据服务** - 提供表单、字段、实体、操作的元数据管理\n3. **通用数据服务** - 提供统一的CRUD操作和查询构建能力\n\n所有接口和类都完全符合云苍穹标准，并且：\n- 函数简洁（不超过50行）\n- 文档完整（完整的XML注释）\n- 易于扩展（事件驱动架构）\n- 易于使用（链式API设计）\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/PLUGIN_USAGE_EXAMPLES.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1791,"output":4488,"cacheRead":54811,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774227573834}}
